snippet.description:
Brown Town Music & Nav Sandhu Presents New Punjabi Song Routine By Gur Sidhu Ft Jasmine Sandlas.

Listen to Routine song on all audio streaming platforms:

Track Credits:-
Song: Routine
Singer: Gur Sidhu Ft Jasmine Sandlas
Lyrics: Kaptaan
Music: Gur Sidhu
Mix & Master: B Sanjh
Concept / screenplay / direction: Garrybhullarfilms 
Dop - shoeb siddiqui 
Associate Director - Bunny khatri(Billa)
Editor - Garrybhullar 
Final Edit - Gobindpuriya 
BTS - Shubby

Label: Brown Town Music
Team Believe Artist Services: https://www.instagram.com/believeasd/


Team Gur Sidhu :
Hair - Abhishek 
Makeup  - Addy 
Costume  - Sruishty Juneja 

Team Jasmine Sandlas :
Hair - Ishan 
Makeup - Addy 
Costume - Priyana thappar
Management - Vaani Jindal

LYRICS:-

Main bathinde di cream te tu cali di queen ae
Krta scan billo jihnu kitta seen ae
Akh vich fire aa te cup ch caffine ae
Munda lagge zehar te tu lagdi zareen ae
Two face duniya imaan te na deen ae
Jo nal yakke turde aa ohna te yakeen ae
Golden kartoos russia di been ae
Khulli aa zmeen billo khulli beggy jean ae
Tuckin shirt aa te lagda shokeen ae

Ni ehtan sada regular mitthiye routine ae x4

Nakhro te noor poora husan hseen ae
Offran tan aoungiya kudi aafreen ae
Tim tim krdi ve age haale teen ae
Jhaaka mera jhaaka jatta surgan da scene ae
Scene j bnaunda jehda kr lainda seen ae
Dirty ja dekhda a teri ki skeem ae
Bhrr peg naina cho j lggea tu peen ae
Theke te na jayi meri akh di toheen ae

Munda....
Blue pinde label joint ch green ae

Ni ehtan sada.......

Ni ehtan sada
Ni ehtan sada

Ehtan sada regular mithiye routine aa x4

Kaptaan kaptaan kaptaan kaptaan nu
Harr koi firdi aa nal laike jaan nu
Ishqy crispy ja jatt dekh dekh k
Sohni ton v sohni pandi gabhru nu khaan nu

Puchde aa saare ve ah khand kitho ayi ae
Bnke poison di pand kitho ayi ae
Gol lakk nach nach vaal khull gye ve
Hoke taquilla nal band kitho ayi ae

Jatt vi oh chkke jihdi age eighteen ae

Ehtan sada regular mithiye routine aa x4

Kaatal queen mainu pyar nal aakh de
Mudke ni labbe kyi mere ch gwaach gye
Mera ki ksoor main v rabb ne bnaai aan
Kyi mainu dekh dekh vigad jwaak gye

Nazaran de nazran na paayi jaawe match ni
Aish cash lekhan ch tu karr farmaish ni
Ik do k habbitan khraab baby sadiyan
Peg vich ice aa te chaa ch black ni

Tu high off hoea firre hookeh da shokeen ae

Ni ehtan sada regular mithiye routine aa x4

#gursidhu #jasminesandlas #punjabisong

Meerabâ€™s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her familyâ€™s decision regarding her and Murtasimâ€™s life. Meerabâ€™s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerabâ€™s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. snippet.title: Tere Bin Episode 33 Teaser - 13th April 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 33 Teaser - 13th April 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerabâ€™s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her familyâ€™s decision regarding her and Murtasimâ€™s life. Meerabâ€™s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerabâ€™s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasimâ€™s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 3741 - Babita Wins a Car?! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | à¤¤à¤¾à¤°à¤• à¤®à¥‡à¤¹à¤¤à¤¾
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri

snippet.description:
Ambedkar Jayanti, also known as Bhim Jayanti, is an annual festival commemorating Dr BR Ambedkar's birthday on April 14, 1891. This year marks the 132nd anniversary of Babasaheb's birth. Dr. Ambedkar was a social reformer, jurist, economist, author, polyglot orator, a scholar, and thinker of comparative religions.

This video covers the given topic, â€˜Dr. B.R. Ambedkarâ€™ in the following structure: 

1. Why in the News?
2. About About Babasaheb Dr. Bhimrao Ambedkar
3. Contribution
4. Election and Designation
5. Important works

localized.title: Dr. B.R. Ambedkar - To The Point | UPSC Current Affairs | Drishti IAS
localized.description:
Ambedkar Jayanti, also known as Bhim Jayanti, is an annual festival commemorating Dr BR Ambedkar's birthday on April 14, 1891. This year marks the 132nd anniversary of Babasaheb's birth. Dr. Ambedkar was a social reformer, jurist, economist, author, polyglot orator, a scholar, and thinker of comparative religions.

This video covers the given topic, â€˜Dr. B.R. Ambedkarâ€™ in the following structure: 

1. Why in the News?
2. About About Babasaheb Dr. Bhimrao Ambedkar
3. Contribution
4. Election and Designation
5. Important works

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3744 - 13 Apr 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3744: Taarak Warns Jethalal
--------------------------------------------------------
Early arrivals Bagha and Nattu Kaka talk about the success of the lucky draw. Additionally, some customers come into Gada Electronics to turn in their coupons. Nattu Kaka advises Bawri to leave the store when she arrives since Jetha dislikes having her there during working hours. She has arrived, says Bawri, to take her Khushi Bhet. Jetha is expected by Nattu Kaka, Bagha, and Bawri, but he arrives a little late. Later, when Jetha calls Mr. Rustom to talk about the coupons, Mr. Rustom compliments Jetha's efforts instead. Additionally, he states that he would like to present him with a certificate of appreciation. The following event is revealed if you watch the show!

----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3743 - 12 Apr 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3743: Coupon Kahan Gaya?
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha and Tapu rush to the washing machine because they believe they mistakenly washed Babita Ji's voucher. Jetha checks his pocket and discovers the damp crippled voucher, which irritates him greatly. Fortunately, Babita Ji wakes up and realizes it was all a nightmare. Babita becomes concerned and phones Jetha for confirmation. Jetha contacts Babita on video and shows her the coupon. She is relieved and returns to sleep. Jetha collects the coupon the next morning in order to submit it to Ramsang Company. Babita inquires about Iyer's coming and, as a result, organizes a surprise. Watch the episode to find out about upcoming events!

----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel. 
              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.

snippet.title: Maharashtra  Politics | à¤…à¤œà¤¿à¤¤ à¤¦à¤¾à¤¦à¤¾à¤‚à¤šà¥€ à¤®à¤µà¤¿à¤†à¤ªà¤¾à¤¸à¥‚à¤¨ à¤«à¤¾à¤°à¤•à¤¤ | Marathi News
snippet.description:
There are indications of a political earthquake again in the politics of Maharashtra. The ruling Shiv Sena is gearing up to shock the opposition BJP. After Shiv Sena's successful revolt against Uddhav Thackeray under the leadership of Eknath Shinde, NCP is likely to get a shock. Some NCP MLAs are said to be in touch with the ruling party. Discussions have started that a group of around 20 MLAs are preparing to revolt against the party.

snippet.title: FAMILY AUR SHAADI KI SHOPPING..!!
snippet.description:
Let's take you men's wear shopping for the festive wedding season at the most happening place in Hyderabad in the Banjara Hills at the Asuka Store

Walk in and experience the medley of heritage and old world charm with the modern, just like their collection, and exult in the ritual of fine dressing, an experience that's gonna leave you savouring in the fragrance of tommorow!

The design house hails from Delhi where they've been manufacturers of men's wear garments for over 35 years. From ceremonial suits for festive occasions, Sherwanis for Weddings, ornate Bandhgalas, Kurtas, indowestern attire in wide range of hues, fabrics, embroidery, and matching shoes and accesories, it's a one stop shop for men who like to dress the best! 

Shop Ethnic and Western Men's wear at Asuka Store 
Visit : Banjara Hills, Road No. 2, Hyderabad

Instagram : @ asukacouture

For Business Inquiry : hyderabaddiaries@yahoo.com

snippet.description:
Episode 3742: Khushi Bhet
--------------------------------------------------------
Champaklal is given an explanation of the lucky draw win by Jetha, Bagha, and Nattu Kaka. Jetha is eager to announce the winner, but Nattu Kaka unintentionally reveals Babita Ji's name. Jetha becomes agitated because he wants to reveal Babita Ji's name. Afterward, Jetha promises to repay Bagha and Nattu Kaka financially for their efforts in the program. On the other side, Madhavi and Anjali experience some disappointment about losing the car. Sonu comforts her mother by promising that she will soon own her ideal vehicle. Babita is also eager about taking driving lessons and getting her license. The following event is revealed if you watch the show!

snippet.description:
The â€˜MTV Hustle 2.0â€™ alum Panther brings to you his first love song â€“ or rather, his first heartbreak song! Featuring Pallavi Deswal, the track is guaranteed to remind you of your ex, and the countless memories associated with them. Perfect to be shared with the one with whom you canâ€™t share anything anymore, â€˜Dard-E-Dilâ€™ is composed, written and sung by Panther.

#DardEDil #Panther #Ankee

Audio Credits
Primary Artist - Panther, Ankee
Writer, Singer, Composer, Rapper - Panther
Producer - Ankee
Additional Guitars - Rapchari

Video credits
Director/ concept - Divyansh Joshi
Creative director - Parth Joshi, Shubham Sharma
Dop - Tushar Gupta, Ashish Bahuguna
Production - Abhimanyu Kochar, Rishabh Pandey, Sanjana Arya.

Spot - Vikas, Abhay
Light - Manthan, Lavi Nahal

Female Lead - Pallavi Deswal
Manoj Joshi, Sambhav Sharma, Simran Bhatt, Ravi Jain, Akshita Oli, Dipsari mondal, Anshita Rawat, Shruti Pokhriyal, Anushka Bora

Project Head - Manoj Joshi
Managed by Sambhav Thakur, Acapella Productions

Lyrics:
Suno mera dard e dil
Usne zakham dia fir wo hanske chal padi
Hum to unke muntazir
Shikwe lakho par 
Chehre pe shikan nahi
Verse

Usne jalaya humko
Mai usse jala kab
Hota Zara bata aisa insaaf kaha par
Daga kar
fir uski dawa kar
Baat bas itni si ki gaya ni tu bata kar
Tumne rulaya humko
Aansu na baha par
Hota Zara bata aisa insaaf kaha par
Jyaada sunaya tune
Aur fir Suna kam
Baat bas itni si ki gaya ni tu bata kar

Padha kar tu mere baare padha kar
Jana hai kya upar leke wafa tujhe bachakar
Hansi gaya fansakar, Hansi gayi bhula kar,
Koi ghayal na chute jab koi chorey galey lagakar,
nazm tere naam pe to deta hu kuch Bada padh
Ho gayi tu kharch, karunga kya itna kama kar
Jyaada sunaya tune
Aur fir Suna kam
Baat bas itni si ki gaya ni tu bata kar

Chorus

Suno mera dard e dil
Usne zakham dia fir wo hanske chal padi
Hum to unke muntazir
Shikwe lakho par 
Chehre pe shikan nahi

 Verse 

Kehna to hai kaafi tumse
Shayad ek baar to mang logi maafi mujhse
Log kehte Hum na reh gaye hai pehle jaise
Shayad tu reh gayi hai kaafi mujhme

Bhari duniya lagti khaali si hai
Na hu akela par akelepan ka sath bhi hai
Tu gayi to chala gaya sukoon bhi
Ab kisi jism me tere jism sa araam ni hai

Chehre kaafi par hai tera chehra nahi,
Kehte sab par koi tumsa kehta nahi,
Rehne ko hai kaafi ghar mere paas
Par na gharme hoti tu to ghar bhi gharsa lagta nahi

Sabkuch paakar bhi sab kho diya hai
Kiya itna sab par tu na to fir kyu kiya hai
Jhagadta na hai mujhse ab koi,
Apne me hu rehta kyuki apno ko hi kho dia hai

Chorus

Suno mera dard e dil
Usne zakham dia fir wo hanske chal padi
Hum to unke muntazir
Shikwe lakho par 
Chehre pe shikan nahi

snippet.description:
De Dollarization | End of US Dollar | Yuan Vs Dollar

Many countries have joined the idea of De Dollarization, the idea to remove the US dollar as the major world reserve currency. Russia and China are leading the e de-dollarization movement by replacing us dollar with the Chinese yuan. This video explains how the US dollar became a world reserve currency, the advantages of becoming the world reserve currency and how the US misused its reserve currency status to manipulate the US economy and sanction countries across the world. The video also explains the progress of the de-dollarization movement over the years including the petroyuan proposed by Saudi Arabia and China, will it lead to the end of us dollar dominance, will the Chinese Yuan replace the US dollar? and the alternative currencies including the BRICS currency.

#dedollarization #chineseyuan #usdollar

snippet.title: KGF Chapter 2 Completes 1 YearðŸ”¥| Yash |Prashanth Neel |Vijay Kiragandur | Sanjay Dutt |Hombale Films
snippet.description:
One year ago today, #KGFChapter2 took us on an unforgettable journey filled with breathtaking action, intense emotions and larger-than-life characters. The film's release was nothing short of a festival, with fans celebrating in theaters around the world. We're humbled by the incredible response to the film and grateful to everyone who made it such a success. Here's to the power of storytelling and the magic of cinema!

Written and Directed by Prashanth Neel
Produced by Vijay Kiragandur under the Banner "Hombale Films".
Starring: Rocking Star Yash, Sanjay Dutt, Srinidhi Shetty, Raveena Tandon, Prakash Raj, Malvika Avinash, Achyuth Kumar, Ayyappa P. Sharma, Rao Ramesh, Eshwari Rao, Archana Jois, T. S. snippet.description:
à¤–à¤¤à¤°à¥‡ à¤®à¥‡à¤‚ Lovely à¤•à¤¾ à¤°à¤¾à¤œà¤¼ | Thapki Pyar Ki | à¤¥à¤ªà¤•à¥€ à¤ªà¥à¤¯à¤¾à¤° à¤•à¥€ | Full Episode | Ep. 681

Despite Aryan's constant suspicion and questions, Lovely hides her identity really well. Her ultimate plan is to throw the Pandey family out of the house. But her plan hits an unexpected roadblock when a man visits the Pandey family and recognises her. Will her identity be exposed?

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

Mujhe Pyaar Hua Tha; What You Want & What Your Destiny Wants

Mujhe Pyaar Hua Tha is a love triangle between Maheer, Saad, and Areeb. Saad has always been in love with his cousin Maheer but when he fails to confess it to her, life takes a different turn

Written By: Sidra Sehar Imran
